org.eclipse.graphiti.mm.algorithms.styles.impl
Class AbstractStyleImpl

java.lang.Object
  EObjectImpl
      org.eclipse.graphiti.mm.algorithms.styles.impl.AbstractStyleImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
AbstractStyle
public abstract class AbstractStyleImpl
extends EObjectImpl
implements AbstractStyle

An implementation of the model object 'Abstract Style'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Background
  • Foreground
  • Line Width
  • Line Style
  • Filled
  • Line Visible
  • Rendering Style
  • Transparency
